{
  "stem": "3283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes I think, did this really happen to me, a kid on the East Side selling newspapers, that eventually I was going to be a judge and go to the Nuremberg trials?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never even dreamed of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a civilian, though.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the beginning, we used to wear uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we said, well, we want to appear to be democratic, so we took the uniforms off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we wore civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "American, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one trial that I mentioned about Neckerman, it was a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lieutenant from-- he was from Texas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wasn't very fair in his questioning of this defendant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I realized that right away, so I took over the questioning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, he was convicted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anybody could come in, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew that these crimes were committed, and they had to pay the consequences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, at the beginning, the first defendants that appeared before me, you know, in the US, you say, are you guilty or not guilty?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the interpreter said, 'Schuldig oder nicht schuldig?'",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they answer 'nicht schuldig,' and they start walking towards the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the military police, they had to grab them back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, you're going to try-- be tried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in most cases, they all said, I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Hitler.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler, he gave the orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody pleaded guilty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not in their code.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all said they had a defense, because we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Hitler that did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
